Patch 8.0.0851
Problem:    'smartindent' is used even when 'indentexpr' is set.
Solution:   Ignore 'smartindent' when 'indentexpr' is set. (Hirohito Higashi)
Files:      src/misc1.c, src/testdi/test_smartindent.vim


